revisions.description: The CISCO-SP-MIB is obsolete and has been replaced by the combination of the CISCO-ITP-TC-MIB and CISCO-ITP-GSP-MIB. Updated the mib to import Unsigned32 from SNMPv2-SMI instead of CISCO-TC. Modified the syntax of CSpRouteTableName and CSpLinksetId to OCTET STRING. Changed the order of objects in cSpAccountingTableEntry SEQUENCE. Added the notification group ciscoSpNotificationsGroup and included it in the MODULE-COMPLIANCE as optional.
Initial version of this MIB module.
